        "content": "<p>There are 84 lean files not in <code>for_mathlib</code>. I've decided that I should start cleaning them up and documenting them.<br>\nI've started with <code>Mbar/bounded.lean</code>. It's gone quite well.</p>\n<p>You will be delighted to know that in the process, two new files were added to <code>for_mathlib</code> <span aria-label=\"crazy\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f61c\" role=\"img\" title=\"crazy\">:crazy:</span></p>",
