        "timestamp": 1624473836
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm quite happy with <code>Mbar/*</code> now. It now has a <code>README.md</code> that you can read over at <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/lean-liquid/tree/master/src/Mbar\">https://github.com/leanprover-community/lean-liquid/tree/master/src/Mbar</a></p>",
